snippet.title: Mega Man 11 - 30th Anniversary Trailer
snippet.description: READY? Mega Man 11 is coming to Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC in late 2018! Take a trip down memory lane and see how Mega Man has evolved in his latest adventure. More details: http://www.capcom-unity.com/capkel/blog/2017/12/04/ready-mega-man-11-is-coming-in-late-2018
